pr_title: GSoC 2019 - port MapMint from Python 2.x to Python 3.x
pr_body:
Summary of all commits:
* Update INSTALL.md
* Port all the python files and optimise the results.
* Port all the python Cheetah template files.
* Recompile template files with Cheetah3
* Change indentation to 4 spaces as per [PEP 8](https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/#indentation) standards.
* Reformat python programs to make them more readable.
* Update jquery v2.0.3 ---> v3.4.1, create symbolic link with name jquery-2.0.3.min.js
* Use "lxml" instead of "libxslt"
* Fix "str" and "unicode" encoding related bugs
* syntax fix in:
    - mapmint-services/vector-tools-src/cgi-env/vectInfo.py
    - mapmint-ui/templates/largemap.tmpl

pr_title: GSoC 2019 - port MapMint from Python 2.x to Python 3.x
pr_body:
Summary of all commits:
* Update INSTALL.md
* Port all the python files and optimise the results.
* Port all the python Cheetah template files.
* Recompile template files with Cheetah3
* Change indentation to 4 spaces as per [PEP 8](https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/#indentation) standards.
* Reformat python programs to make them more readable.
* Update jquery v2.0.3 ---> v3.4.1, create symbolic link with name jquery-2.0.3.min.js
* Use "lxml" instead of "libxslt"
* Fix "str" and "unicode" encoding related bugs
* syntax fix in:
    - mapmint-services/vector-tools-src/cgi-env/vectInfo.py
    - mapmint-ui/templates/largemap.tmpl

pr_title: GSoC 2019 - port MapMint from Python 2.x to Python 3.x
pr_body:
Summary of all commits:
* Update INSTALL.md
* Port all the python files and optimise the results.
* Port all the python Cheetah template files.
* Recompile template files with Cheetah3
* Change indentation to 4 spaces as per [PEP 8](https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/#indentation) standards.
* Reformat python programs to make them more readable.
* Update jquery v2.0.3 ---> v3.4.1, create symbolic link with name jquery-2.0.3.min.js
* Use "lxml" instead of "libxslt"
* Fix "str" and "unicode" encoding related bugs
* syntax fix in:
    - mapmint-services/vector-tools-src/cgi-env/vectInfo.py
    - mapmint-ui/templates/largemap.tmpl

pr_title: GSoC 2019 - port MapMint from Python 2.x to Python 3.x
pr_body:
Summary of all commits:
* Update INSTALL.md
* Port all the python files and optimise the results.
* Port all the python Cheetah template files.
* Recompile template files with Cheetah3
* Change indentation to 4 spaces as per [PEP 8](https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/#indentation) standards.
* Reformat python programs to make them more readable.
* Update jquery v2.0.3 ---> v3.4.1, create symbolic link with name jquery-2.0.3.min.js
* Use "lxml" instead of "libxslt"
* Fix "str" and "unicode" encoding related bugs
* syntax fix in:
    - mapmint-services/vector-tools-src/cgi-env/vectInfo.py
    - mapmint-ui/templates/largemap.tmpl

pr_title: GSoC 2019 - port MapMint from Python 2.x to Python 3.x
pr_body:
Summary of all commits:
* Update INSTALL.md
* Port all the python files and optimise the results.
* Port all the python Cheetah template files.
* Recompile template files with Cheetah3
* Change indentation to 4 spaces as per [PEP 8](https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/#indentation) standards.
* Reformat python programs to make them more readable.
* Update jquery v2.0.3 ---> v3.4.1, create symbolic link with name jquery-2.0.3.min.js
* Use "lxml" instead of "libxslt"
* Fix "str" and "unicode" encoding related bugs
* syntax fix in:
    - mapmint-services/vector-tools-src/cgi-env/vectInfo.py
    - mapmint-ui/templates/largemap.tmpl

pr_title: GSoC 2019 - port MapMint from Python 2.x to Python 3.x
pr_body:
Summary of all commits:
* Update INSTALL.md
* Port all the python files and optimise the results.
* Port all the python Cheetah template files.
* Recompile template files with Cheetah3
* Change indentation to 4 spaces as per [PEP 8](https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/#indentation) standards.
* Reformat python programs to make them more readable.
* Update jquery v2.0.3 ---> v3.4.1, create symbolic link with name jquery-2.0.3.min.js
* Use "lxml" instead of "libxslt"
* Fix "str" and "unicode" encoding related bugs
* syntax fix in:
    - mapmint-services/vector-tools-src/cgi-env/vectInfo.py
    - mapmint-ui/templates/largemap.tmpl
